Title: jQuery Ui Server Controls
Description: JQueryUi Server Controls provide ASP.net MVC server controls which output JQuery UI controls (only tab control at this time).  This ensures that your page is always displayed as you intend & doesn't have a delay while the JQuery UI script is applied, which can look unprofessional
